Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: One City Center is located in the heart of Downtown Durham on a historic site bounded by W. Main, N. Corcoran and W. Parrish Streets. It is also at the epicenter of ongoing and planned development projects, including the 21c Museum Hotel, Aloft Hotel, Unscripted Hotel, Hotel Durham, and five apartment communities totaling more than 1,100 new units.
